playdar.prefPane
================
A Mac OS X Preference Pane for the Playdar music content resolving daemon.

http://www.playdar.org

The prefPane wraps the daemon completely, with built in Sparkle auto-updates,
so you can just get on with resolving content and not worry about the inner
bits.

Fork It!
--------
http://github.com/mxcl/playdar.prefPane/

Build Process
-------------
You'll need to clone the git source for playdar to the same directory as the
prefpane.

$ git clone git://github.com/RJ/playdar.git
$ git clone git://github.com/mxcl/playdar.prefpane.git
$ ls
playdar  playdar.prefpane

Now open playdar.prefpane/playdar.prefPane.xcodeproj and build.

